1) DOMAIN TRACKING LOGIC - SAI HOÀN TOÀN
   Location: MainViewModel.cs:533-561 (OnTimerTick)
   
   Problem:
   - Tất cả domain KHÔNG trong blocklist = focused (SAI!)
   - Chỉ 5 domain block mặc định → 99% website khác = "focused"
   - Không track domain seconds vào _sessionDistractedSeconds
   - App không chặn doom scrolling như mục đích ban đầu
   
   Solution:
   - Implement 3-tier domain classification:
     * ALLOWLIST: Work domains (github, stackoverflow, docs) → focused
     * BLOCKLIST: Distraction domains (social media) → distracted + timeout
     * NEUTRAL: Tất cả khác → DISTRACTED (default deny)
   
   - Track domain usage properly:
     * isFocused = isInAllowlist || inGraceWindow
     * NOT focused = blocked OR neutral
   
   - Add Settings.DomainAllowlist với defaults:
     github.com, stackoverflow.com, docs.microsoft.com, developer.mozilla.org
   
   Files to change:
   - Settings.cs: Add DomainAllowlist property + defaults
   - MainViewModel.cs:533-561: Rewrite domain tracking logic
   - SettingsWindow.xaml: Add allowlist editor UI
   
   Test impact: Pass existing tests, add new tests for allowlist

