2) BREAK BANK - KHÔNG HOẠT ĐỘNG
   Location: DistractionPolicyEngine.cs:110-116 + MainViewModel.cs
   
   Problem:
   - ComputeBreakBank() method tồn tại NHƯNG không bao giờ được gọi
   - Break segments chạy full duration từ ScheduleBuilder
   - Tính năng penalty break không hoạt động
   
   Solution:
   - Add TimerEngine.AdjustCurrentSegmentTime(int seconds) method
   - Call trong MainViewModel.OnPhaseChanged() khi enter Break:
     ```csharp
     if (e.NewPhase == "Break")
     {
         int plannedMinutes = _currentSegments[index].Minutes;
         int distractedMinutes = _sessionDistractedSeconds / 60;
         int adjustedMinutes = _policyEngine.ComputeBreakBank(plannedMinutes, distractedMinutes);
         
         if (adjustedMinutes < plannedMinutes)
         {
             _timerEngine.AdjustCurrentSegmentTime(adjustedMinutes * 60);
             _notificationService.ShowNotification("Break Adjusted", 
                 $"Break reduced to {adjustedMinutes}m due to {distractedMinutes}m distraction");
         }
     }
     ```
   
   Files to change:
   - TimerEngine.cs: Add AdjustCurrentSegmentTime(int seconds)
   - MainViewModel.cs:480-500 (OnPhaseChanged): Add break bank logic
   
   Test impact: Add test for TimerEngine.AdjustCurrentSegmentTime

