     ```
   
   - Add neutral apps category: Explorer.exe, Calculator.exe, Taskmgr.exe
     → Không tính distracted, không tính focused (neutral)
   
   - Improve IsAppAllowed() logic:
     ```csharp
     public bool IsAppAllowed(string processName)
     {
         // Extract filename from full path
         string filename = Path.GetFileName(processName).ToLowerInvariant();
         return _settings.AppAllowlistProcessNames
             .Any(allowed => filename.Contains(allowed.ToLowerInvariant()));
     }
     ```
   
   Files to change:
   - DistractionPolicyEngine.cs: Improve IsAppAllowed()
