4) SESSION RECOVERY - WORKAROUND LOOP
   Location: MainViewModel.cs:771-775 (RestoreSession)
   
   Problem:
   - Dùng while loop để fast-forward timer (HACK)
   - Không set exact remaining time
   - Comment "This is a workaround"
   
   Solution:
   - Add TimerEngine.SetRemainingTime(int seconds) method:
     ```csharp
     public void SetRemainingTime(int seconds)
     {
         if (_state != TimerState.Running) return;
         
         _remainingSeconds = seconds;
         _segmentTotalSeconds = seconds;
         _stopwatch.Restart();
         OnPropertyChanged(nameof(RemainingSeconds));
     }
     ```
   
   - Replace workaround loop:
     ```csharp
     _timerEngine.SetRemainingTime(snapshot.RemainingSecondsInSegment);
     ```
   
   Files to change:
   - TimerEngine.cs: Add SetRemainingTime() method
   - MainViewModel.cs:771-775: Replace loop with method call
   
   Test impact: Add test for SetRemainingTime accuracy

